### **4. 21_LiveFlowPlotter**  
**Description:**  
A live chart utility for visualizing streamed numerical input in real-time.

#### **README.md**
```markdown
# LiveFlowPlotter - Realtime Chart Viewer

LiveFlowPlotter displays any incoming numeric stream as a continuously updating line chart.

## Features
- Smooth chart animation  
- Adjustable frame rate  
- CLI integration  

## Usage
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/21_LiveFlowPlotter.git
cd 21_LiveFlowPlotter
python visualize.py
